==============
l10n_et_base
==============

This module extends the functionality of base models to support Ethiopia
specific localizations. These include:

* Company Name in Ethiopic script
* Partner Name in Ethiopic script
* Rename VAT field to Tax ID
* New field vat_number for the action VAT registration no.

============

To install this module, you need to:

#. Install from Modules list
